  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparing outcomes of individuals treated with Kinesiotape and oval 8 versus quick cast for a&#xD;
      conservatively managed mallet finger injury. Outcomes include DIP joint extension lag,&#xD;
      patient satisfaction and function via the MHQ.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
